Turtle II
Welcome Novean
With 300+ hours of "Voxel precision tool" and lua scripting the Turtle II
is the ultimate upgrade of an already iconic ship.
Designed to maintain off-planet mining sites that are on a 2 week collection cycle.
With deep space exploration in mind the ship is capable to be armed with
e.g. 8 S-size weapons.
Stats:
900T total mass (Fully fueled /250 warpcells/scrap/no cargo)
(Alioth/Sanctuary)
@1g LVL5 pilot skills 3Kt
@1g LVL4 pilot skills 2.7Kt

@0.5g LVL5 pilot skills 5.4Kt
@0.5g LVL4 pilot skills 4.7Kt
Capable of brake landing and hovering with up to 5.5Kt on 1G planets
With 3Kt cargo: sustanation speed 385kmh
3Kt glide reentry on Alioth with LVL4 pilot skills.

1300KL storage (50x 125L/h mining units running for 1 Week)
Up to 3x 400Kl mission package on sub1G planets.
Info:

Recolour all screens and lights -> activate switch -> select colour on touchscreen.
Activate seat-switch or enter pilotseat for shield and ship monitor sync.

L tank for atmospheric / L + M tank for space.
L tanks accessible under hatch, M-space behind front turtle logo.

M-Space tank is only used by extra vertcal boosters and can be left empty.

Innertia matrix is trimmed to 3KT cargo.
The more weigt -> the less off axis rotation you have.

All screens made in lua screen tech and sync with RGB databank.


PNG/SVG/LUA by RyanPryde and T4kler
LUA and Logic:
Seat DB (linked to pilotseat) holds your flight variables from archhud.
Power switch (linked to pilotseat) enables both shield and ship monitor boards.
If switched off the "NOT operator" invertes the signal to close the doors
and retract the forcefields.

- Shield Script from "du-creators.org/makers/Fox Racing".
Modified to sync with RGB data.
- Ship Monitor from "du-creators.org/makers/Aerogics S %26 T Co".
Modified to sync with RGB data to colour 1.

Recolour programming boards only active in coloring process.

- 1. Colour picker "github.com/Dri0m"
Light controls and dump RGB values into databank.
- 2. Ship screens (Container / Fuel / Side windows)
Parameters: side background, signature.
- 3. Signs back (creator / stats / art signs)".
Parameters: signature, background and art text.
- 4. Lights outside
Activates and sync outside lights with RGB data.
- 5. Screens cockpit (cockpit windows / XL engine lights)
Parameters: background and signature.
- 6. SVG Screens (Turtle logo / table background
Parameters: Turtle logo background.


!!! DONT DELETE ANY OF THE SCREENS !!!
